                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7676" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0517</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2090 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一波三折，RK医药销售人员绩效考核改革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A Twisting Journey: RK Pharmaceutical Sales Personnel Performance Appraisal Reform Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘艳巧，张岚，付小雨，张天宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北RK医药贸易有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">RK医药；组织变革；绩效改革；绩效管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">RK Pharmaceutical, organizational change, performance reform, performance management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国医疗卫生体制改革深入推进，政府出台的两票制、医保控费、“4+7”带量采购、“三医联动”、“医联体”、“医共体”等政策使医药流通企业面临更激烈的竞争。在此背景下，医药流通企业如何“以变应变”是一个重要议题。本案例以河北RK医药贸易有限公司销售人员绩效考核改革为主线，讲述了基于市场格局变化和企业发展的内在需求驱动，RK医药依次实施的三次绩效考核改革的动因、遇到的阻力、采取的措施及实施效果，旨在加强学员对绩效考核改革过程的体会和感悟，深化对绩效情境的理解，增强学员对绩效考核改革过程复杂性的认识。案例也可为其他医药流通企业销售人员绩效管理提供参考和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As China&#39;s healthcare system reform deepens, government policies like the two-ticket system, medical insurance cost control, &quot;4+7&quot; volume-based procurement, &quot;Three Medical Unions,&quot; &quot;Medical Consortia,&quot; and &quot;Medical Communities&quot; have intensified competition among pharmaceutical distribution companies. In this context, how pharmaceutical distribution companies adapt to changes has become a crucial issue. This case study focuses on the performance appraisal reform for sales personnel at Hebei RK Pharmaceutical Trading Co., Ltd. It discusses the motivations, obstacles encountered, measures taken, and the results of three sequential performance appraisal reforms driven by changes in the market landscape and internal corporate needs. The aim is to enhance students&#39; understanding and awareness of the performance appraisal reform process, deepen their comprehension of performance situations, and increase their understanding of the complexity of performance appraisal reform. This case study can also serve as a reference and source of inspiration for performance management in other pharmaceutical distribution companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">权变理论；绩效考核系统；平衡计分卡；目标关键成果</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
